556  READ(32,*) (headerwgwaterdist_file(iv),iv=1,ncolumnswgwaterdist) !Get header
557 
558  DO i=1,nlineswgwaterdist
559  READ(32,*) (wgwaterdist_coeff(i,iv),iv=1,ncolumnswgwaterdist)
560  !write(*,*) (WGWaterDist_Coeff(i,iv),iv=1,ncolumnsWGWaterDist)
561  ENDDO
562  CLOSE(32)
563 
564  CALL inputheadercheck(filen)
565 
566  ! Check codes are unique
567  DO i=1,nlineswgwaterdist
568  DO ii=1,nlineswgwaterdist
569  IF(wgwaterdist_coeff(i,cwg_code)==wgwaterdist_coeff(ii,cwg_code) .AND. i/=ii) THEN
570  WRITE(*,*) 'Code',wgwaterdist_coeff(i,cwg_code),'in WithinGridWaterDist.txt not unique!'
571  CALL errorhint(60,filen,wgwaterdist_coeff(i,cwg_code),notused,notusedi)
572  ENDIF
573  ENDDO
574  ENDDO
575 
576  !=======================================================================
577  !=======================================================================
578 
579  !-----------------------------------------------------------------------
580  !SUEWS run information
581  inputmetformat=10 !Input met data file in LUMPS format(1) or SUEWS format(10)
582  laicalcyes=1 !Use observed(0) or modelled(1) LAI
583  ity=2 !Evaporation calculated according to Rutter(1) or Shuttleworth(2)
584  writedailystate = 1 !Daily state file written
585  tstepcount=0
586 
587  t_interval = 3600 !Number of seconds in an hour
588 
589  !Calculate nsh (number of steps per hour) from model timestep (tstep) set in in RunControl
590  nsh_real = t_interval/REAL(tstep,kind(1d0))
591 
592  ! Check nsh is an integer
593  IF(nsh_real==int(nsh_real)) THEN
594  nsh = int(nsh_real)
595  ELSE
596  CALL errorhint(39,'TSTEP must divide into t_INTERVAL exactly.',REAL(tstep,KIND(1d0)),REAL(t_INTERVAL,KIND(1d0)),notUsedI)
597  ENDIF
598 
599  ! Check nsh is reasonable
600  IF(nsh_real<6.OR.nsh_real>60) THEN
601  CALL errorhint(39,'TSTEP is too small or too large.',REAL(tstep,KIND(1d0)),REAL(t_INTERVAL,KIND(1d0)),notUsedI)
602  ENDIF
603 
604  ! Cast integer nsh as nsh_real for use in calculations
605  nsh_real = REAL(nsh,kind(1d0))
606  ! Cast integer tstep as tstep_real for use in calculations
607  tstep_real = REAL(tstep,kind(1d0))
608  ! get integer nsd from nsh for use in AnOHM checking, 20160708 TS
609  nsd=24*nsh
610 
611  !! Check this is still valid for v2016a
612  halftimestep=REAL(tstep_real)/2/(24*3600) !Used in sun_position to get sunpos in the middle of timestep
613 
614  RETURN
615 
616  !-------Possible problems-----------------------------------------------
617 200 CALL errorhint(47,'RunControl.nml',notused,notused,notusedi)
618 201 CALL errorhint(48,'RunControl.nml',notused,notused,notusedi)
619 
620 203 CALL errorhint(47,trim(filechoices),notused,notused,notusedi)
621 
622 300 CALL errorhint(48,trim(filen),notused,notused,notusedi)
623  !-----------------------------------------------------------------------
624 
625  !pause
626 
627 END SUBROUTINE overallruncontrol

1549  CALL suews_interphourlyprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wuautowe,c_hrprofwuautowe)
1550  ! For water use, normalise so the SUM of the multipliers is equal to 1 (profile is multiplied by daily water use)
1551  tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wumanuwd,:) = tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wumanuwd,:) / sum(tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wumanuwd,:))

1554  tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wuautowe,:) = tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wuautowe,:) / sum(tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_wuautowe,:))
1555 
1556  ! Human activity for CO2 calculations
1557  CALL suews_interphourlyprofiles(gridiv,ctp_humactivitywd,c_hrprofhumactivitywd)
1558  CALL suews_interphourlyprofiles(gridiv,ctp_humactivitywe,c_hrprofhumactivitywe)
1559  ! For human activity, check values are between 1 (night) and 2 (day)
1560  IF(any(tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_humactivitywd,:) < 1 .OR. tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_humactivitywd,:) > 2)) THEN
1561  CALL errorhint(70,'Profile value for human activity (WD) exceeds allowed range 1-2.',notused,notused,notusedi)
1562  ENDIF
1563  IF(any(tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_humactivitywe,:) < 1 .OR. tstepprofiles(gridiv,ctp_humactivitywe,:) > 2)) THEN
1564  CALL errorhint(70,'Profile value for human activity (WE) exceeds allowed range 1-2.',notused,notused,notusedi)
1565  ENDIF

2446 SUBROUTINE checkinitial
2447  !Check the parameters in InitialConditions file.
2448  !Modified by HCW 04 Mar 2014, changed soilmoist(is) checks to use names given in InitialConditions
2449  !Added by LJ in 8/2/2013
2450 
2451  USE allocatearray
2452  USE data_in
2453  USE defaultnotused
2454  USE initialcond
2455  USE snowmod
2456  USE time
2457 
2458  IMPLICIT NONE
2459 
2460  !real(kind(1d0)):: pTol !Precision tolerance for range checks
2461 
2462  IF (temp_c0<(temp_c-10).OR.temp_c0>(temp_c+10)) THEN
2463  CALL errorhint(37,'Temp_C0 very different to Tair.', temp_c0, temp_c, notusedi)
2464  ENDIF
2465

2467  IF (lat>40) THEN
2468  IF ((laiinitialevetr>laimin(conifsurf-2)+1.AND.(id<60.OR.id>330)).OR.&
2469  (laiinitialevetr<laimax(conifsurf-2)-1.AND.(id>130.AND.id<244))) THEN

2471  ENDIF
2472  IF ((laiinitialdectr>laimin(decidsurf-2)+1.AND.(id<60.OR.id>330)).OR.&
2473  (laiinitialdectr<laimax(decidsurf-2)-1.AND.(id>130.AND.id<244))) THEN
2474  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialDecTr in InitialConditions file', laiinitialdectr, laimin(decidsurf-2), notusedi)
2475  ENDIF
2476  IF ((laiinitialgrass>laimin(grasssurf-2)+1.AND.(id<60.OR.id>330)).OR.&
2477  (laiinitialgrass<laimax(grasssurf-2)-1.AND.(id>130.AND.id<244))) THEN
2478  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialGrass in InitialConditions file', laiinitialgrass, laimin(grasssurf-2), notusedi)
2479  ENDIF
2480 
2481  ELSEIF (lat<-40) THEN
2482  IF ((laiinitialevetr<laimax(conifsurf-2)-1.AND.(id<60.OR.id>330)).OR.&
2483  (laiinitialevetr>laimin(conifsurf-2)+1.AND.(id>130.AND.id<244))) THEN
2484  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialEveTr in InitialConditions file', laiinitialevetr, laimax(conifsurf-2), notusedi)
2485  ENDIF
2486  IF ((laiinitialdectr>laimax(decidsurf-2)-1.AND.(id<60.OR.id>330)).OR.&
2487  (laiinitialdectr>laimin(decidsurf-2)+1.AND.(id>130.AND.id<244))) THEN
2488  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialDecTr in InitialConditions file', laiinitialdectr, laimax(decidsurf-2), notusedi)
2489  ENDIF
2490  IF ((laiinitialgrass<laimax(grasssurf-2)-1.AND.(id<60.OR.id>330)) .OR.&
2491  (laiinitialgrass>laimin(grasssurf-2)+1.AND.(id>130.AND.id<244))) THEN
2492  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialGrass in InitialConditions file', laiinitialgrass, laimax(grasssurf-2), notusedi)
2493  ENDIF
2494 
2495  ELSEIF (lat<10.AND.lat>-10) THEN
2496 
2497  IF (laiinitialevetr<laimax(conifsurf-2)-0.5) THEN
2498  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialEveTr in InitialConditions file', laiinitialevetr, laimax(conifsurf-2), notusedi)
2499  ENDIF
2500  IF (laiinitialdectr<laimax(decidsurf-2)-0.5) THEN
2501  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialDecTr in InitialConditions file', laiinitialdectr, laimax(decidsurf-2), notusedi)

2503  IF (laiinitialgrass<laimax(grasssurf-2)-0.5) THEN
2504  CALL errorhint(37,'Check LAIinitialGrass in InitialConditions file', laiinitialgrass, laimax(grasssurf-2), notusedi)
2505  ENDIF
2506 
2507  ENDIF
2508 
2509  !Soilstore check
2510  IF (soilstorebldgsstate>soilstorecap(bldgsurf)) THEN
2511  CALL errorhint(37,'InitialCond: Check initial condition of building soil store.',&
